Fourth & Value — Player Props (Week 5)

Select Bet → Game → Player. Optional: Book & search. Sorted by Edge (bps). Line = sportsbook threshold. Book Odds = book's offered price (includes vig). Fair (De-vig) = book price with ~5% vig removed. Book % = book's implied probability (with vig). Model % = our model's probability. Edge = Model % − Book % (basis points). Consensus Line = median line across books. Market % = de-vigged consensus probability across all books. Books = number of books offering this prop.
· Tip: “No Scorer” is hidden.
